OL,3,CTartan Army takes over Miami ahead of
OL,4,CScotland vs Brazil
OL,6,FThe Tartan Army has started to descend
OL,7,Fon the sweltering hot Florida city
OL,8,Fahead of Wednesday's last group stage
OL,9,Fmatch against Brazil, as ITV News'
OL,10,FPeter Scott reports
OL,12,FScotland fans have descended on Miami,
OL,13,FFlorida, for what could be a historic
OL,14,FWorld Cup match against Brazil on
OL,15,FWednesday.
OL,17,FSteve Clarke's side currently sit
OL,18,Fthird in Group C after a 1-0 win and
OL,19,Fdefeat against Haiti and Morocco.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
