PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782305297
OL,3,CTartan Army takes over Miami ahead of
OL,4,CScotland vs Brazil
OL,6,FIf all goes well, Scotland has a
OL,7,Fchance at qualifying for the knockout
OL,8,Fstage at the World Cup for the first
OL,9,Ftime ever, following eight previous
OL,10,Fgroup-stage exits.
OL,12,FThey could even qualify with a loss,
OL,13,Fbut would need to wait until all the
OL,14,Fgroup games finish on June 27 to know
OL,15,Ftheir fate.
OL,17,FDefender and captain Andy Robertson
OL,18,Fadmitted that Brazil will be a tough
OL,19,Fgame, but remained positive, telling
OL,20,Freporters: "We are in control of our
OL,21,Fown destiny."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
