FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782305297
OL,3,CTartan Army takes over Miami ahead of
OL,4,CScotland vs Brazil
OL,6,FHe's certainly got backing from fans,
OL,7,Fas thousands of Tartan Army members
OL,8,Ftravelled to Miami for the game.
OL,10,FFans from both teams were seen
OL,11,Fdrinking, dancing on Ocean Drive, and
OL,12,Fwishing each other luck. Some even
OL,13,Fplayed five-a-sides and other street
OL,14,Ffootball games.
OL,16,F"Everywhere they go, people fall in
OL,17,Flove with them," Robertson said.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
