PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782305297
OL,3,CTartan Army takes over Miami ahead of
OL,4,CScotland vs Brazil
OL,6,F"Come tomorrow night. If we manage to
OL,7,Fbeat Brazil ... I'm sure maybe a
OL,8,Fcouple of beers will be drunk by the
OL,9,FTartan Army. That's for sure," he
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FThe Tartan Army certainly won over the
OL,13,Fhearts of people in Boston, where
OL,14,Ftheir previous games were held, as
OL,15,Fthey marched through the city playing
OL,16,Fbagpipes and chanting the new
OL,17,Funofficial 'No Scotland, No Party'
OL,18,Fanthem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
