OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1782305297
OL,3,CTartan Army takes over Miami ahead of
OL,4,CScotland vs Brazil
OL,6,FBack on home turf, faithfuls will be
OL,7,Fwatching at fan zones across Scotland
OL,8,Fincluding the Ovo Hydro in Glasgow and
OL,9,FThe Pitt in Edinburgh. The game will
OL,10,Fkick off at 11pm UK time.
OL,12,FFirst Minister John Swinney said he
OL,13,Fhas faith that the team can make
OL,14,Fhistory and that they "have the chance
OL,15,Fto make themselves legends tonight".
OL,17,FBoth teams kick off at 11pm UK time
OL,18,Fand the game will be available to
OL,19,Fwatch on BBC 1.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
